    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 88.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Erudition</p><p>Prerequisite: Arcane Savant</p><p>You automatically identify the school, casting time, maximum duration and general effects of spells being cast within 60 feet of you, or ongoing spells whose effects you can sense. When you are forced to make a saving throw against a spell you’ve identified in this way, you can use your reaction to gain advantage on the roll. Additionally, you learn 3 spells of up to 7th level from any spellcasting list. They count as spells of your class for you.</p></div>",
